  "Using only astronomical observations": "",
  "Studying only the social media response": "",
  "Applying nuclear physics principles alone": "",
  "The Flint water crisis involved corrosive water chemistry leaching lead from pipes (chemistry), health impacts of lead exposure (public health), aging infrastructure failures (civil engineering), and regulatory failures (environmental policy), demonstrating the need for interdisciplinary analysis.": "",
  "The study of coral reef bleaching events requires integration of which scientific fields?": "",
