  "The discovery that chlorofluorocarbons (CFCs) caused ozone depletion led to the Montreal Protocol. Which scientific discipline first identified the chemical mechanism of ozone destruction?": "",
  "Geology": "",
  "Atmospheric chemistry": "",
  "Paleontology": "",
  "Marine biology": "",
